name: Feather Boa Recedes
description: When the Feather Boa recedes it creates a vacuum, pulling in the next available object...The Habaneros! Taken from my collab with Tanutispidercat for our live streamed performance at Vidicon. This clip is straight out of my video feedback diorama. It is 100% live with no aftereffects..Just cameras pointing at screens, intermixed with video synthesis. The video diorama is motorized with 3 motion controlled turntables. The main camera is a GoPro that is motion controlled to pan back and forth..
